      | How to create your list of ingredients

    p.govuk-body
      | If you notify using exact concentrations or concentration ranges, you need
        to create a document which lists the cosmetic product’s ingredients:

    ul.govuk-list.govuk-list--bullet
      li for every new notification
      li where a product’s formulation has changed significantly

